defaultModern intensive a
defaultgriculture faces many environmental problems – soil degradation and erosion, water pollution and excess demand for irrigation, loss of agricultural biodiversity. In addition it faces social problems – l
defaultoss of rural jobs and livelihoods and undermining of local 
defaultand traditional knowledge of ecosystem management
default, sustainable agriculture and genetic resources for food and agriculture
