defaultpolicy campaign
default 
defaultwith their proposal to reintroduce the conversion of food waste into feed for pig production, using approved cooking processes that render it safe for use as feed by killing any 
defaultpathogens present such as foot and mouth disease and classical swine fever. DEFRA is encouraged to work with the Pig Idea and BPEX to implement this initiative, already common in other countries such as Japan, South Korea, China and many states in the USA
